<div id="review_1342427391" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1342427391" />
    <a title="Spencer Rich" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/9226864-spencer-rich"><img alt="Spencer Rich" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1581637117p2/9226864.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1342427391?book_show_action=true">Jul 22, 2015</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Spencer Rich" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Spencer Rich" href="/user/show/9226864-spencer-rich">Spencer Rich</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1342427391" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer9348467237151706787">This book is truly amazing. A funny, cynical tale with quite a lot of theosophical symbolism. Amazing that it survived the onslaught of Christianity. For a book from the second century A.D., it&apos;s a surprisingly modern novel, incorporating lots of great short stories better than the much later Canterbury Tales.</span>
  <span id="freeText9348467237151706787" style="display:none">This book is truly amazing. A funny, cynical tale with quite a lot of theosophical symbolism. Amazing that it survived the onslaught of Christianity. For a book from the second century A.D., it's a surprisingly modern novel, incorporating lots of great short stories better than the much later Canterbury Tales.</span>
  <a data-text-id="9348467237151706787" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
